# Project audit guidance — AUDITOR prompt preamble (example stub)

Copy this file to `audit-preamble.md` (drop the `.example`) and REPLACE the body below with your project's
standing rules for the independent AUDITOR. Its contents are injected into **every** auditor prompt —
unconditionally, once the file exists. Absent → no output → identical to stock.

Use it for always-applies verification rules the auditor must honor on every task.

